text: The 1889 Georgetown football team represented the Georgetown University during the 1889 college football season. Georgetown finished the season with a 5–1 record. This season included the first match against a full collegiate team, Virginia. Georgetown's records show this game as a 34–0 victory for the them, while Virginia's record a 32–0 victory for the Cavaliers. ==Schedule== ==References== Georgetown Category:Georgetown Hoyas football seasons Georgetown football
